Installation 

cd 
git clone https://github.com/jamescasbon/vimrc .vim
ln -s .vim/vimrc .vimrc
cd .vim
git submodule init && git submodule update


Launch vim and run :BundleInstall

Command-t needs to be built: 

  cd bundle/command-t && rake make

needs rubygem-make, rubygem-bundle

Install pyflakes, pylint or flake8 for python syntax checking

    pip install --user flake8


